    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>百样物品</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">使用数百样物品构筑自己的推币机，保龄球，迪斯科球，或者西瓜。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065710/extras/0ca86238b6b2539d098386c8fb55dea6.poster.avif?t=1770052063\" width=780 height=378 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065710/extras/0ca86238b6b2539d098386c8fb55dea6.webm?t=1770052063\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065710/extras/0ca86238b6b2539d098386c8fb55dea6.mp4?t=1770052063\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>多种角色</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">多种不同机制的角色可供选择，从每局胜利的游戏中获得G-Coin，为角色解锁新服装以及新能力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065710/extras/c5eb7417bb24f0a425447bda80c16c34.avif?t=1770052063\" width=1540 height=756 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>贴纸与道具</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">贴纸与道具给每一局带来不同体验,，贴纸用于强化物品，道具可以全局发挥作用。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065710/extras/1bdf20ccd8d93ee4a9ac71aa8f923cdb.avif?t=1770052063\" width=780 height=379 /></span></p>",
